WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

2
00:03:11.791 --> 00:03:14.487
Cheers!

3
00:03:22.402 --> 00:03:23.801
Excellent.

4
00:03:24.370 --> 00:03:26.600
Let's drink until we drop.

5
00:03:26.906 --> 00:03:28.533
Save something for your wife.

6
00:03:28.775 --> 00:03:31.505
Are you kidding?

7
00:03:31.878 --> 00:03:34.210
Alcohol revives me.

8
00:03:34.414 --> 00:03:36.974
The later it gets. the hornier I get.

9
00:03:37.316 --> 00:03:40.945
Another glass. A little sip.

10
00:03:44.190 --> 00:03:45.953
Tell me. Jane...

11
00:03:46.492 --> 00:03:47.789
What year are you in?

12
00:03:48.161 --> 00:03:48.820
4th year.

13
00:03:49.028 --> 00:03:51.223
A senior should know better.

14
00:03:51.464 --> 00:03:53.898
What are you doing with Tun?

15
00:03:54.333 --> 00:03:55.561
He's a hunk.

16
00:03:55.802 --> 00:03:58.270
You keep saying that.

17
00:03:58.504 --> 00:04:01.132
Making Jim ask for girl's numbers.

18
00:04:01.374 --> 00:04:02.102
Then breaking their hearts.

19
00:04:02.341 --> 00:04:05.674
Speaking of broken hearts...

20
00:04:05.878 --> 00:04:07.277
Remember the time...

21
00:04:07.480 --> 00:04:10.711
that girl left him a drunken mess.

22
00:04:11.050 --> 00:04:12.017
Her name was Kay.

23
00:04:12.251 --> 00:04:13.912
Ignore them.

24
00:04:15.888 --> 00:04:17.981
Wait. I have a question.

25
00:04:18.291 --> 00:04:20.156
How can a guy like you get married?

26
00:04:20.359 --> 00:04:21.792
What's wrong with me?

27
00:04:22.495 --> 00:04:25.055
After a long tiring day...

28
00:04:25.431 --> 00:04:26.989
I want to head home...

29
00:04:27.333 --> 00:04:29.631
to a wife's embrace or a pet's face.

30
00:04:29.836 --> 00:04:31.303
Not waste my life...

31
00:04:31.871 --> 00:04:33.930
partying with you losers.

32
00:04:34.173 --> 00:04:35.800
Not with me.

33
00:04:36.709 --> 00:04:37.801
A good man...

34
00:04:38.244 --> 00:04:40.576
who went whoring with me last night.

35
00:04:42.148 --> 00:04:43.809
Fooling around so soon?

36
00:04:45.218 --> 00:04:46.480
Here she comes.

37
00:04:49.021 --> 00:04:49.680
Quiet.

38
00:04:49.889 --> 00:04:50.947
What's so funny?

39
00:04:52.692 --> 00:04:53.681
Nothing.

40
00:04:54.126 --> 00:04:56.390
One last thing...

41
00:04:57.129 --> 00:04:59.029
One more glass!

42
00:05:18.084 --> 00:05:19.381
What are we listening to?

43
00:05:21.687 --> 00:05:22.881
Don't turn it off.

44
00:05:23.089 --> 00:05:24.420
It's beautiful.

45
00:05:27.093 --> 00:05:28.788
You guys seem tight.

46
00:05:29.028 --> 00:05:30.620
Do you meet often?

47
00:05:34.400 --> 00:05:35.526
What are you looking at?

48
00:05:36.335 --> 00:05:37.700
Beautiful you.

49
00:05:40.072 --> 00:05:41.300
What a sap.

50
00:06:23.416 --> 00:06:24.883
Are you hurt?

51
00:06:26.619 --> 00:06:27.881
Tun...

52
00:06:28.821 --> 00:06:30.345
Is she dead?

53
00:06:38.698 --> 00:06:40.063
Wait!

54
00:06:49.609 --> 00:06:50.803
Drive away.

55
00:06:51.477 --> 00:06:53.104
I said drive away!

56
00:06:54.313 --> 00:06:55.712
Drive away!

57
00:07:05.891 --> 00:07:07.688
Get closer. please.

58
00:07:08.294 --> 00:07:09.261
Okay.

59
00:07:10.296 --> 00:07:11.729
Big smile. Nuch.

60
00:07:12.531 --> 00:07:13.828
Or you won't look pretty.

61
00:07:22.141 --> 00:07:23.665
All Science Majors...

62
00:07:23.909 --> 00:07:26.104
gather for a class photo.

63
00:07:26.612 --> 00:07:27.840
They're calling you.

64
00:07:28.881 --> 00:07:30.007
Where's Jane?

65
00:07:31.450 --> 00:07:33.884
Taking photos with her friends.

66
00:07:35.021 --> 00:07:37.182
I though maybe you broke up.

67
00:07:38.090 --> 00:07:39.682
Come! Let's go.

68
00:08:34.847 --> 00:08:36.940
I phoned but you didn't pick up.

69
00:08:37.316 --> 00:08:38.476
Was it on silent?

70
00:08:47.493 --> 00:08:49.120
Nuch asked about you today.

71
00:08:52.498 --> 00:08:54.261
When will you be free?

72
00:08:54.500 --> 00:08:56.400
She wants to...

73
00:09:17.790 --> 00:09:18.984
Jane.

74
00:09:20.726 --> 00:09:22.387
How can you act like this?

75
00:09:26.232 --> 00:09:28.223
Pretending nothing happened.

76
00:09:30.402 --> 00:09:31.528
Since that night...

77
00:09:31.771 --> 00:09:33.363
I haven't slept soundly.

78
00:09:37.309 --> 00:09:39.004
I'm upset as well.

79
00:09:41.080 --> 00:09:43.412
At least we should have checked.

80
00:09:45.317 --> 00:09:47.478
It was an accident.

81
00:09:48.754 --> 00:09:50.415
That's easy for you to say.

82
00:09:51.924 --> 00:09:53.653
You weren't behind the wheel.

83
00:10:05.771 --> 00:10:07.295
- Hi. Ti.
- Hey.

84
00:10:07.840 --> 00:10:09.603
How's business?

85
00:10:09.909 --> 00:10:11.877
With you here this early...

86
00:10:12.278 --> 00:10:14.178
business should be bad.

87
00:10:15.915 --> 00:10:17.712
Are my prints ready?

88
00:10:18.651 --> 00:10:20.380
Yeah. Just a sec.

89
00:10:25.291 --> 00:10:26.349
Here.

90
00:10:49.648 --> 00:10:50.945
Is your processor broken?

91
00:10:52.451 --> 00:10:53.577
Let's see.

92
00:10:58.390 --> 00:10:59.652
The nerve.

93
00:10:59.859 --> 00:11:01.224
Nice prints and you're great.

94
00:11:01.427 --> 00:11:03.861
If they suck. it's my fault.

95
00:11:04.230 --> 00:11:05.629
Let's check the negative.

96
00:11:06.599 --> 00:11:07.827
No way.

97
00:11:08.033 --> 00:11:09.364
I took them. I should know.

98
00:11:09.602 --> 00:11:10.694
We'll see.

99
00:11:13.072 --> 00:11:14.164
See.

100
00:11:15.474 --> 00:11:17.135
Your negative are bad.

101
00:11:40.299 --> 00:11:41.459
Tun.

102
00:11:51.710 --> 00:11:53.109
Tun.

103
00:12:09.795 --> 00:12:11.092
Tun.

104
00:12:13.098 --> 00:12:14.531
Can you hear me?

105
00:14:18.323 --> 00:14:19.620
Help!

106
00:14:20.692 --> 00:14:22.250
Help!

107
00:14:54.893 --> 00:14:57.361
Don't be scared. I'm here now.

108
00:15:17.082 --> 00:15:18.447
What's wrong with your camera?

109
00:15:19.785 --> 00:15:20.752
I don't' know.

110
00:15:20.953 --> 00:15:22.477
The whole roll is ruined.

111
00:15:25.124 --> 00:15:26.819
That many?

112
00:15:32.531 --> 00:15:34.089
What are these shadows?

113
00:15:35.134 --> 00:15:36.795
My camera must be broken.

114
00:15:38.871 --> 00:15:40.600
How should I tell Nuch?

115
00:15:44.543 --> 00:15:45.840
Tun...

116
00:15:47.312 --> 00:15:48.711
Look at this picture.

117
00:15:59.858 --> 00:16:01.018
That woman...

118
00:16:02.161 --> 00:16:03.492
Do you think she's dead?

119
00:16:04.229 --> 00:16:05.287
That's enough.

120
00:16:10.602 --> 00:16:12.900
I'll have my camera fixed tomorrow.

121
00:17:15.300 --> 00:17:16.130
Tun...

122
00:17:16.335 --> 00:17:17.666
Look at this picture.

123
00:17:41.493 --> 00:17:43.051
Are you sure it was here?

124
00:17:50.302 --> 00:17:51.200
Excuse me.

125
00:17:51.403 --> 00:17:52.370
What happened?

126
00:17:52.804 --> 00:17:56.205
A few days ago a car hit the billboard.

127
00:17:56.642 --> 00:17:57.870
Must have been drunk.

128
00:17:59.878 --> 00:18:01.846
Was anyone hurt?

129
00:18:02.881 --> 00:18:03.973
No.

130
00:18:04.516 --> 00:18:05.847
Just the broken sign.

131
00:18:06.084 --> 00:18:07.381
Are you sure?

132
00:18:07.619 --> 00:18:08.483
What?

133
00:18:09.955 --> 00:18:11.513
Nothing.

134
00:18:12.824 --> 00:18:14.018
Thank you.

135
00:18:15.994 --> 00:18:17.086
What?

136
00:18:19.264 --> 00:18:21.391
You sure you checked everywhere?

137
00:18:24.903 --> 00:18:26.200
Nothing.

138
00:18:26.872 --> 00:18:28.100
Thanks anyways.

139
00:18:32.978 --> 00:18:35.378
He called every precinct and hospital.

140
00:18:36.982 --> 00:18:40.418
No accidents were reported that night.

141
00:18:40.819 --> 00:18:42.218
That's not possible.

142
00:18:43.422 --> 00:18:45.151
What about the girl we hit?

143
00:18:46.825 --> 00:18:49.055
You sure he called every one?

144
00:18:49.328 --> 00:18:51.091
Maybe someone helped her.

145
00:18:51.663 --> 00:18:53.528
Maybe she's fine.

146
00:18:53.799 --> 00:18:55.164
How could she be fine?

147
00:18:55.400 --> 00:18:57.163
We ploughed her down.

148
00:19:00.172 --> 00:19:01.833
And even if she's fine...

149
00:19:03.442 --> 00:19:05.103
Something is in those pictures.

150
00:19:05.577 --> 00:19:08.205
I told you they're not related to her.

151
00:19:08.714 --> 00:19:09.840
They're just bad exposures.

152
00:19:10.048 --> 00:19:11.481
Get it?

153
00:20:12.911 --> 00:20:13.935
Tun...

154
00:20:14.613 --> 00:20:16.205
You need to make some merit.

155
00:20:17.682 --> 00:20:18.842
These pictures...

156
00:20:19.217 --> 00:20:21.412
show that a spirit is haunting you.

157
00:20:27.692 --> 00:20:30.092
How long have you been a photographer?

158
00:20:30.295 --> 00:20:31.922
Why are you showing me these?

159
00:20:32.264 --> 00:20:33.162
I know...

160
00:20:33.665 --> 00:20:35.792
But don't you find these shadows strange?

161
00:20:38.303 --> 00:20:39.600
You want to see spirits?

162
00:20:40.605 --> 00:20:41.833
I'll show you some.

163
00:20:49.815 --> 00:20:50.543
Here.

164
00:20:51.249 --> 00:20:52.375
Auntie Cham's spirit.

165
00:20:53.385 --> 00:20:54.682
You know where she is now?

166
00:20:57.689 --> 00:21:00.453
She's selling grilled bananas next door.

167
00:21:02.160 --> 00:21:03.491
Here's Auntie Cham. And here.

168
00:21:04.229 --> 00:21:05.287
All Auntie Cham.

169
00:21:05.831 --> 00:21:07.025
Taken on the same day.

170
00:21:07.399 --> 00:21:08.559
They're just double exposures...

171
00:21:08.800 --> 00:21:10.267
and out of focus.

172
00:21:11.203 --> 00:21:14.001
Come on. I know that.

173
00:21:22.314 --> 00:21:24.407
Everyone is familiar with this place.

174
00:21:25.951 --> 00:21:28.215
Just an ordinary location...

175
00:21:29.588 --> 00:21:31.180
that we pass...

176
00:21:31.790 --> 00:21:33.280
and see everyday.

177
00:21:38.830 --> 00:21:40.695
Now look at these pictures...

178
00:21:44.603 --> 00:21:47.401
taken of the same place.

179
00:21:48.240 --> 00:21:49.502
In these...

180
00:21:50.642 --> 00:21:52.200
the bridge looks nicer.

181
00:21:54.412 --> 00:21:55.674
That means photography...

182
00:21:56.114 --> 00:22:00.380
does not reproduce reality.

183
00:22:02.721 --> 00:22:04.018
It depends on how...

184
00:22:05.023 --> 00:22:07.617
the image is framed.

185
00:22:08.226 --> 00:22:09.716
What is revealed.

186
00:22:10.095 --> 00:22:11.722
What is concealed.

187
00:22:12.931 --> 00:22:15.525
Your perspective is critical.

188
00:22:26.878 --> 00:22:30.405
"Special Scoop: Spirit Pictures"

189
00:22:42.894 --> 00:22:44.293
Jane. you're early.

190
00:22:46.765 --> 00:22:47.993
I'll get it.

191
00:22:53.004 --> 00:22:54.665
- Hello?
- Hello. Tun.

192
00:22:54.906 --> 00:22:56.874
It's Jane. I'll come by later.

193
00:22:58.310 --> 00:22:59.004
Hello?

194
00:22:59.244 --> 00:23:01.303
Tun. can you hear me?

195
00:23:01.546 --> 00:23:02.774
Hello?

196
00:23:02.981 --> 00:23:04.243
Tun!

197
00:23:04.482 --> 00:23:05.744
Tun!

198
00:23:06.484 --> 00:23:07.542
Hello?

199
00:23:07.752 --> 00:23:09.276
Hello?

200
00:23:36.648 --> 00:23:37.910
What's wrong?

201
00:23:38.717 --> 00:23:39.684
I don't' know.

202
00:23:39.884 --> 00:23:41.852
My neck's hurt since the accident.

203
00:23:42.921 --> 00:23:44.582
You should go see a doctor.

204
00:23:46.491 --> 00:23:47.753
I'm sure it's not serious.

205
00:23:51.196 --> 00:23:52.823
What's the use of talking to these spoofs?

206
00:23:54.499 --> 00:23:56.990
"Real Ghosts"

207
00:23:59.504 --> 00:24:00.903
Are you a reporter?

208
00:24:01.172 --> 00:24:02.196
No.

209
00:24:03.274 --> 00:24:05.742
The funeral foundation sent us.

210
00:24:07.979 --> 00:24:10.174
We run a legal operation.

211
00:24:10.482 --> 00:24:12.245
We have all the right permits.

212
00:24:59.731 --> 00:25:00.789
Excuse me.

213
00:25:01.232 --> 00:25:03.530
Are all these pictures fakes?

214
00:25:05.170 --> 00:25:07.502
Piak! Tell the boss he has guests.

215
00:25:10.341 --> 00:25:11.672
Everyone fakes them.

216
00:25:13.178 --> 00:25:14.202
You know...

217
00:25:14.479 --> 00:25:16.344
these photos are always a hit.

218
00:25:17.515 --> 00:25:19.506
Any issue with them sells out.

219
00:25:20.585 --> 00:25:21.552
But you think...

220
00:25:21.986 --> 00:25:23.681
we can always find real ones?

221
00:25:25.957 --> 00:25:28.118
Isn't that deceiving the public?

222
00:25:29.527 --> 00:25:31.222
Our readers...

223
00:25:31.863 --> 00:25:33.854
want to see scary photos.

224
00:25:35.200 --> 00:25:36.758
They don't want loves stories.

225
00:25:38.503 --> 00:25:41.904
Does that mean every photo is fake?

226
00:25:45.009 --> 00:25:46.840
I didn't say that.

227
00:26:00.391 --> 00:26:01.517
Take a look.

228
00:26:02.494 --> 00:26:03.893
See anything?

229
00:26:04.529 --> 00:26:06.827
This is the first photo I had.

230
00:26:08.066 --> 00:26:09.431
I took it at home.

231
00:26:11.202 --> 00:26:12.430
The shadow...

232
00:26:12.704 --> 00:26:15.172
bears a likeness to my mom.

233
00:26:18.510 --> 00:26:20.205
Believe what you will.

234
00:26:22.313 --> 00:26:23.405
But this picture...

235
00:26:24.215 --> 00:26:27.048
was taken after she passed away.

236
00:26:29.053 --> 00:26:30.452
You know...

237
00:26:30.722 --> 00:26:31.711
sometimes...

238
00:26:31.923 --> 00:26:34.357
spirits long for their loved ones.

239
00:26:40.598 --> 00:26:41.963
In my opinion...

240
00:26:42.834 --> 00:26:44.131
these pictures...

241
00:26:45.303 --> 00:26:46.770
represent more than...

242
00:26:47.405 --> 00:26:49.373
macabre urban legends.

243
00:26:51.609 --> 00:26:53.804
They are signs.

244
00:26:58.416 --> 00:26:59.713
Think about it.

245
00:27:01.019 --> 00:27:02.509
Why would the dead...

246
00:27:03.288 --> 00:27:04.880
return to the living...

247
00:27:08.259 --> 00:27:11.126
Without a message to convey?

248
00:27:15.433 --> 00:27:16.798
Most importantly...

249
00:27:17.702 --> 00:27:19.101
I believe...

250
00:27:20.171 --> 00:27:21.604
these shadows...

251
00:27:22.340 --> 00:27:24.808
are related to someone in the picture.

252
00:27:29.080 --> 00:27:30.342
A father...

253
00:27:30.715 --> 00:27:31.773
mother...

254
00:27:32.083 --> 00:27:33.414
or lover.

255
00:27:35.520 --> 00:27:36.782
Or someone...

256
00:27:36.988 --> 00:27:38.979
you maligned in life.

257
00:28:01.946 --> 00:28:04.608
How can we tell if they're real...

258
00:28:04.816 --> 00:28:06.147
and not fakes?

259
00:28:06.517 --> 00:28:07.950
What about Polaroid's?

260
00:28:08.152 --> 00:28:09.551
Can you fake them?

261
00:28:12.991 --> 00:28:17.360
You load the film and press the shutter.

262
00:28:17.795 --> 00:28:19.092
The photo ejects.

263
00:28:36.915 --> 00:28:38.576
Tell me then...

264
00:28:39.350 --> 00:28:41.284
How can they be faked?

265
00:28:45.223 --> 00:28:47.817
How do we know what they want?

266
00:28:48.426 --> 00:28:49.415
Perhaps...

267
00:28:49.694 --> 00:28:51.525
the answer is in the photo.

268
00:29:02.006 --> 00:29:03.871
Two more poses.

269
00:29:04.742 --> 00:29:06.175
Big smiles.

270
00:29:10.014 --> 00:29:12.574
Let's have a different pose.

271
00:29:13.217 --> 00:29:16.118
Embrace her. hold the bouquet...

272
00:29:16.321 --> 00:29:18.346
and kiss her cheek.

273
00:29:20.725 --> 00:29:21.783
Beautiful.

274
00:29:23.361 --> 00:29:25.226
We're done.

275
00:29:25.596 --> 00:29:27.962
Thank you both.

276
00:29:28.399 --> 00:29:30.594
Take them to the dressing room.

277
00:29:55.927 --> 00:29:57.258
What the...

278
00:29:59.063 --> 00:30:00.325
Who's doing that?

279
00:30:00.898 --> 00:30:02.331
Aum. check the fuse!

280
00:30:04.235 --> 00:30:05.634
Hey! Aum!

281
00:30:08.773 --> 00:30:09.603
Aum!

282
00:30:10.875 --> 00:30:12.001
Who's doing that?

283
00:30:13.277 --> 00:30:15.245
Is it you. Aum?

284
00:30:21.519 --> 00:30:22.679
Who is it?

285
00:30:25.356 --> 00:30:26.846
Aum. where are you?

286
00:30:28.893 --> 00:30:30.360
Who's there!

287
00:30:31.029 --> 00:30:32.291
I asked who it is!

288
00:30:40.371 --> 00:30:41.963
Where are you. Aum?

289
00:30:47.211 --> 00:30:48.610
Who's there!

290
00:31:37.862 --> 00:31:39.454
Please step off the scale.

291
00:31:43.034 --> 00:31:44.626
Step on it again.

292
00:31:52.443 --> 00:31:54.070
Been working hard lately?

293
00:31:54.312 --> 00:31:55.802
Not really.

294
00:31:56.447 --> 00:31:57.880
How long has it hurt?

295
00:31:58.850 --> 00:32:00.681
For quite awhile.

296
00:32:00.885 --> 00:32:02.750
But it's gotten worse lately.

297
00:32:03.221 --> 00:32:05.382
I had a car accident.

298
00:32:05.990 --> 00:32:07.252
