302
00:32:16.901 --> 00:32:19.062
Your x-rays are normal.

303
00:32:19.403 --> 00:32:20.927
It may be a sprain.

304
00:32:21.272 --> 00:32:23.331
Try the medicine I prescribed.

305
00:32:24.642 --> 00:32:26.701
Mr. Tun. please pick up your prescription.

306
00:32:30.681 --> 00:32:31.909
Take this medicine...

307
00:32:32.283 --> 00:32:34.547
3 times a day after meals...

308
00:32:34.819 --> 00:32:37.049
until the prescription runs out.

309
00:32:39.090 --> 00:32:40.284
Lying bastard.

310
00:32:41.492 --> 00:32:42.288
Pardon?

311
00:32:42.493 --> 00:32:43.551
Yes?

312
00:32:44.896 --> 00:32:46.386
Nothing.

313
00:32:51.035 --> 00:32:52.696
Lying bastard.

314
00:32:54.405 --> 00:32:55.702
Lying bastard.

315
00:32:56.841 --> 00:32:58.308
As for this medicine...

316
00:33:00.244 --> 00:33:00.903
Sir!

317
00:33:01.145 --> 00:33:03.010
What's wrong?

318
00:33:06.017 --> 00:33:07.575
...is rarely seen.

319
00:33:08.085 --> 00:33:10.519
When grasshoppers begin mating...

320
00:33:11.022 --> 00:33:13.957
the male smells the female...

321
00:33:14.759 --> 00:33:18.354
from a distance up to 100 meters.

322
00:33:19.163 --> 00:33:22.758
The male carefully approaches the female.

323
00:33:23.534 --> 00:33:26.594
It hooks itself onto her belly.

324
00:33:27.305 --> 00:33:29.102
And they begin to mate.

325
00:33:30.708 --> 00:33:34.405
The female's response is surprising.

326
00:33:35.580 --> 00:33:38.947
The male becomes her prey.

327
00:33:39.584 --> 00:33:43.213
She slowly eats off his head...

328
00:33:43.788 --> 00:33:46.348
while they are mating.

329
00:33:48.259 --> 00:33:49.248
Eventually...

330
00:33:49.460 --> 00:33:51.621
the male succumbs to death.

331
00:34:00.304 --> 00:34:03.603
Excuse me. where is Room 301?

332
00:34:09.947 --> 00:34:10.845
Jane.

333
00:34:14.885 --> 00:34:16.318
Jane.

334
00:34:25.763 --> 00:34:27.025
Jane.

335
00:35:35.900 --> 00:35:37.060
Who's there?

336
00:36:05.730 --> 00:36:06.856
Tonn...

337
00:36:07.765 --> 00:36:09.130
What's wrong?

338
00:36:12.703 --> 00:36:13.670
Tun...

339
00:36:13.871 --> 00:36:15.304
I'm going to die.

340
00:36:15.506 --> 00:36:17.133
What's going on?

341
00:36:17.808 --> 00:36:18.900
The photos...

342
00:36:20.511 --> 00:36:21.944
Bring me those photos.

343
00:36:23.013 --> 00:36:24.207
What photos?

344
00:36:24.482 --> 00:36:25.506
Are you drunk?

345
00:36:27.184 --> 00:36:28.515
Those photos...

346
00:36:28.953 --> 00:36:30.477
Where did you hide them?

347
00:36:30.721 --> 00:36:32.018
Give them to me.

348
00:36:33.724 --> 00:36:35.157
Remember that bitch.

349
00:36:35.426 --> 00:36:36.415
Calm down.

350
00:36:37.561 --> 00:36:38.391
What photos?

351
00:36:38.596 --> 00:36:40.223
Just give them to me!

352
00:36:40.598 --> 00:36:42.293
Please calm down.

353
00:36:43.501 --> 00:36:44.900
Tonn. calm down.

354
00:36:45.703 --> 00:36:47.102
What photos?

355
00:36:52.243 --> 00:36:53.403
Tonn.

356
00:36:53.611 --> 00:36:55.044
I'll call your wife.

357
00:37:37.888 --> 00:37:39.116
What are you doing?

358
00:37:40.658 --> 00:37:42.182
Cleaning up.

359
00:37:48.265 --> 00:37:49.698
Your neck still sore?

360
00:37:51.702 --> 00:37:52.862
Yeah.

361
00:37:53.103 --> 00:37:55.162
Take it easy. Don't work so much.

362
00:42:25.309 --> 00:42:27.106
"Natrenapa Chan-ngam. Honor Society 1995"

363
00:42:39.490 --> 00:42:40.650
Tonn.

364
00:42:41.492 --> 00:42:42.982
It's Tun.

365
00:42:44.595 --> 00:42:46.062
Are you home?

366
00:43:00.210 --> 00:43:01.302
Tonn.

367
00:43:03.614 --> 00:43:05.104
Are you home?

368
00:43:13.924 --> 00:43:15.084
Tonn.

369
00:43:39.783 --> 00:43:41.011
"Natrenapa Chan-ngam"

370
00:44:28.131 --> 00:44:29.621
Tonn!

371
00:44:30.334 --> 00:44:31.426
Tonn!

372
00:44:33.303 --> 00:44:34.463
Tonn!

373
00:44:41.411 --> 00:44:42.901
Tonn!

374
00:45:18.516 --> 00:45:21.280
I'm really sorry.

375
00:45:22.587 --> 00:45:23.815
Do you know...

376
00:45:24.055 --> 00:45:25.522
What was bothering him?

377
00:45:29.394 --> 00:45:30.918
No. Suddenly he...

378
00:45:31.129 --> 00:45:33.359
It's your gang's fault.

379
00:45:35.700 --> 00:45:37.429
Have you all gone insane?

380
00:45:38.736 --> 00:45:40.328
What do you mean?

381
00:45:41.506 --> 00:45:43.474
You've all committed suicide.

382
00:45:44.809 --> 00:45:45.935
Who?

383
00:45:47.345 --> 00:45:48.778
Don't you know?

384
00:45:49.447 --> 00:45:50.914
The other two...

385
00:45:51.315 --> 00:45:53.340
also killed themselves.

386
00:45:54.052 --> 00:45:55.280
Which two?

387
00:45:58.556 --> 00:46:02.356
The two who sat next to you.

388
00:46:46.671 --> 00:46:48.104
Who's this woman?

389
00:46:52.477 --> 00:46:53.876
Where did you get that?

390
00:46:55.146 --> 00:46:57.205
She's the shadow in the photos. right?

391
00:46:58.850 --> 00:47:00.010
Who is she?

392
00:47:02.920 --> 00:47:04.888
How is she related to you?

393
00:47:23.241 --> 00:47:25.209
I knew her in college.

394
00:47:28.312 --> 00:47:29.802
Her name is Natre.

395
00:47:33.384 --> 00:47:35.375
She was a quiet person...

396
00:47:37.121 --> 00:47:38.486
without any friends.

397
00:47:42.627 --> 00:47:44.492
We all thought she was weird.

398
00:47:49.667 --> 00:47:51.259
I felt sorry for her.

399
00:47:58.509 --> 00:48:00.704
We dated but I kept it secret.

400
00:48:04.248 --> 00:48:05.613
She loved me a lot.

401
00:50:56.787 --> 00:50:58.482
She threatened to slit her wrists.

402
00:51:00.291 --> 00:51:01.918
I didn't know what to do.

403
00:51:02.493 --> 00:51:04.188
My friends thought it was funny.

404
00:51:04.695 --> 00:51:06.219
How were they involved?

405
00:51:06.764 --> 00:51:08.061
Why are they dead?

406
00:51:08.666 --> 00:51:09.792
They...

407
00:51:10.000 --> 00:51:11.058
What did they do?

408
00:51:13.504 --> 00:51:14.732
I don't know.

409
00:51:16.107 --> 00:51:18.473
Tonn said he'd take care of it.

410
00:51:22.413 --> 00:51:24.108
After that. Natre disappeared.

411
00:51:25.950 --> 00:51:27.975
I never saw her again.

412
00:51:28.986 --> 00:51:31.079
Didn't you try to stop them?

413
00:51:33.190 --> 00:51:35.852
How could you let it happen?

414
00:51:42.400 --> 00:51:43.890
What could I do?

415
00:51:46.303 --> 00:51:47.930
Now everyone is dead.

416
00:51:51.475 --> 00:51:52.703
I'm...

417
00:51:53.677 --> 00:51:55.201
I'm going to die next.

418
00:52:33.951 --> 00:52:35.248
It's funny how...

419
00:52:37.588 --> 00:52:39.488
we always say...

420
00:52:40.424 --> 00:52:42.187
if we could turn back time...

421
00:52:43.961 --> 00:52:44.893
we...

422
00:52:45.129 --> 00:52:47.097
we would reverse all our wrongs.

423
00:52:50.501 --> 00:52:52.128
Do you think she's okay?

424
00:52:53.571 --> 00:52:54.936
Will she be there?

425
00:52:55.372 --> 00:52:56.464
Go to sleep.

426
00:52:59.076 --> 00:53:00.566
I'll keep you company tonight.

427
00:55:05.202 --> 00:55:06.362
Excuse me.

428
00:55:07.671 --> 00:55:09.104
Do you have any toilet paper?

429
00:55:44.108 --> 00:55:45.507
Can I poo first?

430
00:55:45.709 --> 00:55:47.108
I'm sorry.

431
00:56:56.246 --> 00:56:57.474
What's bothering you?

432
00:57:11.328 --> 00:57:12.886
Tun. What's wrong?

433
00:57:25.008 --> 00:57:26.373
What is it?

434
00:58:18.028 --> 00:58:19.290
Is it around here?

435
00:58:30.207 --> 00:58:31.504
Excuse me.

436
00:58:32.109 --> 00:58:33.371
Do you know where this is?

437
00:58:37.781 --> 00:58:39.681
Mom. where is this house?

438
00:59:13.650 --> 00:59:14.912
Ma'am.

439
00:59:27.431 --> 00:59:28.523
Excuse me...

440
00:59:28.765 --> 00:59:30.164
Is this Natre's house?

441
00:59:32.135 --> 00:59:33.295
What do you want?

442
00:59:34.605 --> 00:59:35.629
Well...

443
00:59:36.006 --> 00:59:38.167
We're her friends.

444
00:59:39.142 --> 00:59:41.133
Natre's friends? Come inside.

445
00:59:52.222 --> 00:59:54.690
Have some water. You must be tired.

446
00:59:55.025 --> 00:59:56.617
Did you drive from Bangkok?

447
00:59:57.828 --> 00:59:58.852
Yes.

448
01:00:01.965 --> 01:00:05.992
We'd like to ask about Natre.

449
01:00:07.037 --> 01:00:08.698
She's not feeling well.

450
01:00:09.106 --> 01:00:10.403
She's taking a nap.

451
01:00:11.909 --> 01:00:13.308
Should I wake her?

452
01:00:17.681 --> 01:00:19.273
Stay for dinner.

453
01:00:20.150 --> 01:00:21.378
I was about to cook.

454
01:00:21.585 --> 01:00:23.951
I'm making her favourite dish.

455
01:00:25.656 --> 01:00:27.214
Natre will be so happy.

456
01:00:27.724 --> 01:00:29.555
Her friends don't visit often.

457
01:00:30.160 --> 01:00:31.559
Wait right here.

458
01:00:50.514 --> 01:00:51.776
Where are you going?

459
01:02:06.423 --> 01:02:07.720
How dare you?

460
01:02:13.764 --> 01:02:15.732
Did she commit suicide?

461
01:02:20.670 --> 01:02:22.797
We should cremate her.

462
01:02:24.741 --> 01:02:25.708
No.

463
01:02:25.909 --> 01:02:27.274
I won't cremate her.

464
01:02:29.713 --> 01:02:30.702
Ma'am...

465
01:02:32.349 --> 01:02:35.216
I don't know if you believe such things...

466
01:02:35.685 --> 01:02:39.052
but I'd like you to look at these photos.

467
01:02:39.856 --> 01:02:43.189
They were taken around campus.

468
01:02:45.495 --> 01:02:47.827
Some of the places...

469
01:02:48.598 --> 01:02:51.499
were rooms Natre had been in.

470
01:02:52.335 --> 01:02:56.271
And these shadows appeared

471
01:02:59.843 --> 01:03:01.071
I think that...

472
01:03:02.312 --> 01:03:05.406
Natre's spirit is restless.

473
01:03:06.883 --> 01:03:08.111
Natre...

474
01:03:11.755 --> 01:03:13.222
My dear Natre.

475
01:03:15.425 --> 01:03:17.325
Why don't you visit me?

476
01:03:25.802 --> 01:03:28.202
Can you tell me what happened?

477
01:03:29.106 --> 01:03:30.767
Why she left Bangkok?

478
01:03:39.282 --> 01:03:40.544
Ma'am...

479
01:03:42.786 --> 01:03:43.946
Ma'am.

480
01:03:45.322 --> 01:03:46.949
These shadows...

481
01:03:47.524 --> 01:03:50.857
might mean her spirit is not at peace.

482
01:03:55.198 --> 01:03:57.393
We should hold her funeral.

483
01:03:58.935 --> 01:04:00.266
Please.

484
01:04:14.451 --> 01:04:15.679
When she came home...

485
01:04:15.886 --> 01:04:17.319
she seemed different.

486
01:04:17.687 --> 01:04:19.450
She wouldn't talk to anyone.

487
01:04:20.023 --> 01:04:22.014
No one knows what happened in Bangkok.

488
01:04:23.994 --> 01:04:26.155
Then she overdosed on pills.

489
01:04:26.863 --> 01:04:29.263
Luckily. her mother found her...

490
01:04:29.633 --> 01:04:31.498
and got her to the hospital on time.

491
01:04:32.002 --> 01:04:34.266
When she recovered...

492
01:04:35.605 --> 01:04:38.472
she climbed on the hospital roof...

493
01:04:39.109 --> 01:04:40.633
and jumped off the edge.

494
01:04:42.812 --> 01:04:45.576
Why wouldn't her mom cremate her?

495
01:04:47.684 --> 01:04:50.915
She's been distraught
ever since Natre's death.

496
01:04:51.655 --> 01:04:55.318
No matter what she refused to cremate her.

497
01:04:56.660 --> 01:04:58.855
All the villagers were scared.

498
01:04:59.229 --> 01:05:02.027
No one wanted to socialize with her.

499
01:07:04.754 --> 01:07:05.982
Can't sleep?

500
01:07:11.795 --> 01:07:13.854
Tell me the truth...

501
01:07:14.831 --> 01:07:16.492
Did you love Natre?

502
01:07:20.303 --> 01:07:22.032
I tried to...

503
01:07:28.311 --> 01:07:30.802
I believed that one day I would.

504
01:07:36.553 --> 01:07:38.453
But I was fooling myself.

505
01:07:46.463 --> 01:07:47.896
When I broke it off...

506
01:07:49.132 --> 01:07:51.566
I was a total asshole.

507
01:07:57.574 --> 01:07:59.508
But she still loved me the same.

508
01:08:06.082 --> 01:08:07.913
I want this to be over.

509
01:08:09.986 --> 01:08:12.420
If she wants me to die I will.

510
01:08:13.490 --> 01:08:15.151
Don't say that.

511
01:08:16.159 --> 01:08:17.751
It's almost over.

512
01:08:19.129 --> 01:08:20.255
No it's not.

513
01:08:25.435 --> 01:08:27.699
I know she'll come for me.

514
01:08:28.605 --> 01:08:29.663
Tun.

515
01:08:30.573 --> 01:08:32.234
We've come this far.

516
01:08:34.577 --> 01:08:36.545
And you're sorry for what you did.

517
01:08:37.514 --> 01:08:39.072
I'm sure she knows.

518
01:08:41.451 --> 01:08:43.078
Don't talk about death anymore.

519
01:08:50.193 --> 01:08:51.592
I'm sorry.

520
01:08:57.233 --> 01:08:58.996
Do you still love me?

521
01:09:04.941 --> 01:09:07.774
No matter what you won't leave me. right?

522
01:10:46.976 --> 01:10:49.001
Jane.

523
01:12:22.105 --> 01:12:23.402
Tun...

524
01:12:23.773 --> 01:12:24.762
Jane...

525
01:12:25.308 --> 01:12:26.798
Where did you go?

526
01:12:28.111 --> 01:12:29.601
Why did you leave me alone?

527
01:12:30.513 --> 01:12:31.605
We've got to leave.

528
01:12:35.218 --> 01:12:36.617
Asshole!

529
01:12:37.854 --> 01:12:39.321
Why did you leave me?

530
01:12:39.522 --> 01:12:41.217
Didn't you love me?

531
01:12:41.658 --> 01:12:42.955
How could you leave me?

532
01:12:46.029 --> 01:12:47.894
How could you leave me?

533
01:14:27.230 --> 01:14:28.424
Tun...

534
01:14:28.798 --> 01:14:30.356
Are you feeling better?

535
01:14:32.902 --> 01:14:34.893
What happened last night?

536
01:14:36.372 --> 01:14:37.430
Tun...

537
01:14:39.108 --> 01:14:40.075
Jane...

538
01:14:40.276 --> 01:14:41.402
Jane...

539
01:14:48.551 --> 01:14:49.483
The abbot said...

540
01:14:49.685 --> 01:14:51.653
Natre will be cremated today.

541
01:14:55.291 --> 01:14:56.849
It's over.

542
01:16:52.742 --> 01:16:54.300
- Hello.
- Hello. Jane.

543
01:16:54.911 --> 01:16:55.935
Picking up photos?

544
01:16:56.746 --> 01:16:57.644
Where's Tun?

545
01:16:57.847 --> 01:16:59.075
He's busy.

546
01:16:59.548 --> 01:17:00.640
Good.

547
01:17:00.850 --> 01:17:01.680
When he's busy...

548
01:17:01.884 --> 01:17:03.351
I get to see you.

549
01:17:11.460 --> 01:17:12.791
You went on vacation?

550
01:17:13.629 --> 01:17:14.687
To the beach.

551
01:17:15.231 --> 01:17:16.357
When did you go?

552
01:17:17.066 --> 01:17:18.590
Last week.

553
01:17:20.937 --> 01:17:22.928
This photo is...

554
01:17:26.442 --> 01:17:27.602
What's wrong?

555
01:17:33.783 --> 01:17:35.011
You look fatter.

556
01:17:37.386 --> 01:17:38.785
I didn't recognize you.

557
01:17:41.290 --> 01:17:42.257
Hi.

558
01:17:43.259 --> 01:17:44.453
Jumbo prints.

559
01:17:46.162 --> 01:17:47.390
Write you name. please.

560
01:20:26.856 --> 01:20:28.118
Get her guys!

561
01:21:03.792 --> 01:21:04.884
Jane...

562
01:21:05.294 --> 01:21:07.023
Why are you crying?

563
01:21:09.932 --> 01:21:11.024
Asshole...

564
01:21:13.636 --> 01:21:15.604
How could you be so cruel?

565
01:21:21.243 --> 01:21:22.676
Where did you find these?

566
01:21:25.281 --> 01:21:26.873
If I didn't find them...

567
01:21:27.082 --> 01:21:29.312
I'd be a fool forever. right?

568
01:21:34.924 --> 01:21:36.414
Let me explain.

569
01:21:39.662 --> 01:21:41.357
What's there to say?

570
01:21:45.701 --> 01:21:47.293
I always believed you.

571
01:21:54.410 --> 01:21:56.344
I thought I knew you.

572
01:22:10.326 --> 01:22:11.384
Tun.

573
01:22:12.628 --> 01:22:13.754
Take her picture...

574
01:22:14.029 --> 01:22:15.223
so she doesn't blab.

575
01:22:15.431 --> 01:22:17.422
Tun. help me.

576
01:22:19.101 --> 01:22:20.261
I know it was wrong.

577
01:22:21.904 --> 01:22:23.701
Take her picture now!

578
01:22:24.873 --> 01:22:25.999
What's wrong!

579
01:22:27.543 --> 01:22:29.010
I'm your buddy!

580
01:22:29.511 --> 01:22:30.535
Hurry!

581
01:22:39.221 --> 01:22:41.052
Tun. help me.

582
01:22:54.503 --> 01:22:55.800
I never forgave myself.

583
01:22:56.005 --> 01:22:57.973
But I was young and stupid.

584
01:22:59.541 --> 01:23:00.906
I've heard enough.

585
01:23:03.012 --> 01:23:04.502
I'm going home.

586
01:23:59.401 --> 01:24:00.732
Come on out!

587
01:24:05.541 --> 01:24:06.906
Where are you?

588
01:24:13.449 --> 01:24:15.076
I thought you loved me!

589
01:24:17.419 --> 01:24:19.114
Loved me so much!

590
01:24:26.595 --> 01:24:28.790
Till death do us part!

591
01:24:33.902 --> 01:24:35.529
She's gone now.

592
01:26:14.803 --> 01:26:16.031
Sometimes...

